review_content:
I have to say this is a very noble, feminine, and pleasantly subtle women's fragrance - not a girly perfume. It may sound like that, but there’s no "but".... just a convincing message from me about this new perfume;
The first spray brings light fruitiness and a lot of Ylang-Ylang. A tropical flower that promises fine sensuality. The whole thing is elegantly underlined with a floral touch that subtly recedes into the background. After about half an hour, everything becomes very creamy due to the vanilla and musk; it gives me a clean, creamy feeling. Personally, I feel clean, fresh, and in an extremely noble and elegant way, kissed sensually by the scent. It quickly becomes close to the skin; it could last a moment longer for me; I would say about 5 good hours, then it noticeably bids farewell, which is a pity because I find it beautiful. There have been some compliments from gentlemen but also from ladies, it stands out very positively. The large white bottle with the golden accents is just super pretty and a real eye-catcher!
My tip to the gentlemen reading this.... perhaps a new, very noble and elegantly sensual-clean favorite companion for the lady of your heart. Prices are moderate; I chose this companion because it is so clean, different, and elegantly sexy!
